Cleveland Cavaliers Win Lottery, Right to Pick First in June 23 NBA Draft

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-05-18T00:54:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/cleveland-cavaliers-win-lottery-right-to-pick-first-in-june-23-nba-draft.html
The  Cleveland Cavaliers  won the NBA
draft lottery tonight, giving them the right to select first in
the National Basketball Association draft on June 23.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
